  ## Verification Steps                                                                                                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  1. **Database**: Run `npx prisma migrate dev` and verify new tables                                                                                                                     
  2. **Backend**: Test all fees endpoints via Postman                                                                                                                                     
  3. **Frontend**:                                                                                                                                                                        
  - Verify batch creation works                                                                                                                                                           
  - Test hard delete in Danger Zone                                                                                                                                                       
  - Check theme text visibility in both modes                                                                                                                                             
  - Test fee receipt creation (single & bulk)                                                                                                                                             
  - Verify student can see their receipts                                                                                                                                                 
  4. **Build**: Run `npm run build` in frontend - ensure no TypeScript errors                                                                                                             
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ---                                                                                                                                                                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  ## Execution Order                                                                                                                                                                      
                                                                                                                                                                                          
  1. Fix breaking issues first (Part 1A, 1B, 1C)                                                                                                                                          
  2. Run build to verify fixes                                                                                                                                                            
  3. Database migration (Phase 2A)                                                                                                                                                        
  4. Backend fees implementation (Phase 2B)                                                                                                                                               
  5. Frontend types (Phase 2C)                                                                                                                                                            
  6. Frontend Redux API (Phase 2D)                                                                                                                                                        
  7. Frontend UI components (Phase 2E)                                                                                                                                                    
  8. Postman update (Phase 2F)                                                                                                                                                            
  9. Cleanup files (Phase 2G)                                                                                                                                                             
  10. Final build verification                                                                                                                                                            
                                 